<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>ʿlyạ bdrạn, lynạ qsṭẗ</author>
<hymn_number>7320</hymn_number>
<title>mqtũ ạlḥḍyḍ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mqt ạlḥḍyḍ sỷmt ạlrmạl mllt ạlklạm wsw̉ ạlfʿạl ạ̉ryd bdylạaⁿ ljhd ʿqym fnfsy ttwq lqmm ạljbạl
 2- mqt ạlẓlạm sỷmt ạlhmwm mllt ạllyạly bdwn njwm
 ạ̉ryd rjạʾ lqlb klym fnfsy ttwq lfrḥ ydwm
 3-mqt ạlsjwn sỷmt ạlqywd mllt ạlḍyạʿ wṣd ạlsdwd
 ạ̉ryd ạnṭlạqạaⁿ bsyr ḥtẖytẖ fnfsy ttwq lḥfẓ ạlʿhwd
 4- mqt ạlrkwd sỷmt ạlksl mllt ạlḥyạẗ bdwn ạ̉ml
 ạ̉ryd qrạrạaⁿ yạ̉by̱ ạlrjwʿ ʿn jhd ydwm bgẖyr mll
 5- fyạ rby ạ̉nt ḥṣny ạlḥṣyn wạ̉nt ạlḥbyb ạlwạʿd ạlạmyn
 ậty ạ̹lyk bqly sẖgẖwf fạjʿl nṣyby mʿ ạlgẖạlbyn</lyrics>
</song>